  Dear player,
    Welcome to the ShadowGate realms. We appreciate the fact 
    that you have desided to play this MUD. It is one of the best
    AD&D muds around. We try to keep as faithfull to the
    manuals as possible to ensure 100% playing pleasure.
    If you have questions you can post your questions on
    the available boards or ask the wizards and admins online.
    They all should be able to help you .

    We have many areas open and have several quests for
    you to solve. Other challenges are provided as well.

Thank you all very much.
